2:T71b,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is SDL Trados better than Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. SDL Trados scores 7.0 overall while Unbabel scores 7.0. SDL Trados is best for professional translators and enterprises, while Unbabel excels for customer support teams and global companies."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, SDL Trados or Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"SDL Trados starts at $285/year and Unbabel starts at Custom.   Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from SDL Trados to Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both SDL Trados and Unbabel support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about SDL Trados vs Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, SDL Trados holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 4/10. Unbabel has an overall rating of 7/10 and ease of use score of 7/10. Users praise SDL Trados for industry standard with largest market share and Unbabel for human-quality translation at scale."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, SDL Trados or Unbabel?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend SDL Trados for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Unbabel remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize human-quality translation at scale. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div"